# Info

Invoked when rendering the right side of the F3 debug screen, allowing you to add custom debug lines.

# Available Methods

- `event.add(text)` - Add a line to the debug screen

# Example

```js
ClientEvents.rightDebugInfo(event => {
	event.add('Custom Info: World!')
	event.add(`Biome: ${event.player.block.biomeId}`)
})
```
